                    "company": "Vriesendorp & Gaade",
                    "description": "Since 2010, I am one of the partners of Vriesendorp & Gaade.\n\nVriesendorp & Gaade provides legal services since 1833. More than 180 years, we help people and enterprises in protecting their proprietary technologies, their valuable brands and designs, and their good name against misuse, unauthorised use or copying. In addition we help our clients to establish legal agreements with respect to authorised use or licences if so desired, and to defend their technologies in case they are accused of infringement. \n\nOur clients benefit from our expertise and specialist services in any field of Intellectual Property, particularly in the field of patents, trademarks, designs, copyrights, plant breeders' rights and litigation related thereto. These services are provided by our highly trained European and Dutch Patent Attorneys, Trademark Attorneys and experienced staff. In addition, our in-house Attorneys at Law are readily available to defend your rights in case of conflicts or infringement.\n\nWe strive to have direct contact with our clients. Direct contact with our clients enables us to understand the needs of our clients and to properly handle all their Intellectual Property cases. Our European and Dutch Patent Attorneys, Trademark Attorneys and Attorneys at Law can take care of your Intellectual Property in Europe, and in particular in the Netherlands. In addition we assist in obtaining Intellectual Property rights also in the rest of the World via our extensive network of local agents in almost all countries. \n\nWe can help you to stay in control of your proprietary technologies, brands and designs.",
